Plan Description
        
MacAndrews & Forbes Group, LLC Savings or Cash Option Plan for Employees is a defined contribution plan with a profit-sharing component and 401k feature. This plan has a BrightScope Rating of 82, placing it in the top 15% of all plans in its peer group. This plan is also in the top 15% of plans for Account Balances and Salary Deferral. MacAndrews & Forbes Group, LLC Savings or Cash Option Plan for Employees currently has over 300 active participants and over $36.2M in plan assets. 

        

